{"tid":1089224,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有腸易激綜合症？","createTime":"2019-04-02T15:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T11:12:44.000Z","uid":114631,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"631a342349b84a20a8d92caea713439207040844","tid":1089224,"uid":114631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:29:36.000Z","msg":"我係肚瀉型<br />\n依一兩年腸胃都好差<br />\n無論食乜都好似完全無吸引過就屙返出黎<br />\n食飽我諗半個鐘就會屙 <br />\n最痴線試過一日去6-8次廁所都有<br />\n試過去完無耐轉頭又急<br />\n跟住肚漲漲咁<br />\n最大問題係無論食咩都係咁 ....<br />\n戒曬麵包 牛奶 芝士涷野好耐都不斷屙<br />\n食白烚既野都會屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係吹漲<br />\nBtw我個人係長期有運動習慣 <br />\n每次做gym都好比心機咁操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但依排腸胃更加差 根本完全吸收唔到 <br />\n個人keep住好瘦好瘦<br />\n無論食幾多野都無作用...<br />\n做幾多都無用 好灰<br />\n有無人明我感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c515896164cabc98717260c75079ef3667a05be","tid":1089224,"uid":144201,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:33:19.000Z","msg":"有，呢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e6eb569d6dc34e905eebb3dfec84082c6ff5ff","tid":1089224,"uid":95637,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:37:29.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係朝早<br />\n食麵包都凶多吉少"},{"pid":"30c0a611967f6fd876ae0f740b9bd89f0c3fde1d","tid":1089224,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":26,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:37:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係朝早<br />\n食麵包都凶多吉少</blockquote><br />\n兇"},{"pid":"e41c9fc28ac0c0f7e75890fcc651e19bc328ee0e","tid":1089224,"uid":206137,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"戒牛奶 芝士反而間唔中都有食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食益生菌<br />\n<br />\n不過自己經驗覺得最重要係壓力 有一排發左癲噤嘜都唔敢食嘜都計住 唔敢亂出街驚搵廁所 情況反而更差<br />\n<br />\n壓力同心情好大影響 一壓力大就黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86a0dadd596b8707115f5dc71fa91c1a53510be","tid":1089224,"uid":47228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:42:46.000Z","msg":"試下食太田胃散"},{"pid":"5da58b2168ca733c6ee5f0ee09987a7cb4bb0e2c","tid":1089224,"uid":114631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e86a0dadd596b8707115f5dc71fa91c1a53510be","tid":1089224,"uid":47228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:42:46.000Z","msg":"試下食太田胃散"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:44:26.000Z","msg":"我今日買左益生菌唔知有無作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455b8f05d3018f27316a5ce08a2180b04e52ecf0","tid":1089224,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:45:11.000Z","msg":"我似係"},{"pid":"85c30de10eacb1f420efeec8ef6b48bf873fd92f","tid":1089224,"uid":114631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e41c9fc28ac0c0f7e75890fcc651e19bc328ee0e","tid":1089224,"uid":206137,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"戒牛奶 芝士反而間唔中都有食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食益生菌<br />\n<br />\n不過自己經驗覺得最重要係壓力 有一排發左癲噤嘜都唔敢食嘜都計住 唔敢亂出街驚搵廁所 情況反而更差<br />\n<br />\n壓力同心情好大影響 一壓力大就黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:45:44.000Z","msg":"其實我都唔知自己叫唔叫有壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我平時成日做運動<br />\n又無乜壓力都唔知點解會咁"},{"pid":"27e919f3ad5377fe4bd88fa04a3f478d4fc33d76","tid":1089224,"uid":114631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e41c9fc28ac0c0f7e75890fcc651e19bc328ee0e","tid":1089224,"uid":206137,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"戒牛奶 芝士反而間唔中都有食<img src=\"/assets/f