":"2019-04-02T16:29:18.000Z","msg":"其實我一直睇緊順勢治癒 係有效<br />\n但好貴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都一樣肥唔到 增唔到磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355616f42cf8dfdc8cc345fed4f7326fa327b3e6","tid":1089224,"uid":45025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T16:41:18.000Z","msg":"有無食藥？<br />\n<br />\n我幾年前幾嚴重，<br />\n直頭唔想出街<br />\n<br />\n之後睇醫生食藥，<br />\n加埋自我心理調整，<br />\n到而家唔洗食藥，<br />\n係出門去定廁所，<br />\n上午total去兩至三次，<br />\n基本上成日都唔會有問題"},{"pid":"0d37a2626b3afbe00e5c1a166e97c09c5f2c2d96","tid":1089224,"uid":118776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T16:48:53.000Z","msg":"有左13年<br />\n飲水都柯<br />\n有時唔肚痛就會唔自在 驚係條街會突然痛<br />\n然後就會即刻痛到拿住拿住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9040d8e6823466464a7af8cd72a137f2c07b3a0e","tid":1089224,"uid":141871,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:02:34.000Z","msg":"Hi樓主<br />\n情況同你一樣<br />\n開頭以為自己腸易激<br />\n後尾私家醫生建議去照腸鏡<br />\n發現自己有慢性腸炎<br />\n要長期食藥控制免疫系統<br />\n依家好返好多"},{"pid":"6c2875fcb92a11ae58cb70287c4d370f57673e5c","tid":1089224,"uid":180124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:04:01.000Z","msg":"飲一杯咖啡屙4次算唔算<br />\n幾爽個肚冇野塞住"},{"pid":"77c00b54e175a1742e76396ce39a12e822b2b037","tid":1089224,"uid":2986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:07:01.000Z","msg":"check check係咪炎性腸病好喎"},{"pid":"3d79b5660c0cfbf644fe13952c2b7cc7ad543e20","tid":1089224,"uid":204429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:09:02.000Z","msg":"益生菌調理下？"},{"pid":"1441eda2dc8a22120dc18e785bb9c31a101e42de","tid":1089224,"uid":167857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:17:10.000Z","msg":"有！但無確診過<br />\n煩到答車番工都形住形住會痛<br />\n食完飯 基本上都要去廁所<br />\n搞到街都唔想出 去遠門 答長途車必定要食定止痾藥<br />\n照左腸無問題"},{"pid":"5b21af612c123e14623c7ce40576df3c74e49722","tid":1089224,"uid":166368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:26:12.000Z","msg":"曾經試過，不過應該係因為有壓力先有，之後無咁大壓力就好啲，少左肚痛！"},{"pid":"eb641a6aeefa0fb250e2eab911bfab629789bb1a","tid":1089224,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:28:38.000Z","msg":"兩年前有<br />\n個陣壓力大就算冇食野個心諗到都要去廁所<br />\n而家有特別事緊張都會想去廁所但冇以前咁誇張<br />\n<br />\n樓主係屋企個時有冇都keep住要去廁所？"},{"pid":"5c17152110fa23906eb766188e3adb6b9b7f34a5","tid":1089224,"uid":46622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:45:43.000Z","msg":"有 出世到而家都係日日肚屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04dbd0fbce66f484d6ffde1afde7251a2db3010","tid":1089224,"uid":46622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c17152110fa23906eb766188e3adb6b9b7f34a5","tid":1089224,"uid":46622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:45:43.000Z","msg":"有 出世到而家都係日日肚屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:46:31.000Z","msg":"去旅行最少屙5次以上"},{"pid":"30a01dfe22bfe4fcacccdd6230fe39a032d17fd9","tid":1089224,"uid":203172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T18:17:16.000Z","msg":"有，睇左中醫之後好翻好多，間唔中屙一兩次但唔影響生活，之前唔敢搭巴士"},{"pid":"f3ba7df2bc87108aa80e9782354457cfc7117819","tid":1089224,"uid":41943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T19:37:32.000Z","msg":"日日放屁整濕條底褲 算唔算"},{"pid":"c8237747f090709913055e2dab779afec717c4b4","tid":1089224,"uid":86337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T19:43:54.000Z","msg":"一日閒閒地痾三次 一起身一定要痾左先出門<br />\n<br />\n以前都係排骨 以家飲得啤酒多都肥左 特別係肚腩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7be96789aef169f424e44d99c9b943f9fa5758b","tid":1089224,"uid":244904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T21:12:13.000Z","msg":"有 混合型<br />\n仲會成日肚脹 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 